label: AB4C8_cF52_216_a_e_2e-001
title: Room Temperature GaMo$_{4}$S$_{8}$ Structure
comments:
This is the room temperature structure. Below 45K GaMo$_{4}$S$_{8}$ transforms into a \href{current_web_home_dir/AB4C8_hR13_160_a_ab_2a2b-001}{rhombohedral structure}. 
 (Ben Yaich, 1984) do not give the lattice constant for GaMo$_{4}$S$_{8}$.  We infer it from their interatomic distances and obtain a value of a = 9.7294{\AA}.  The ICSD entry uses a = 9.74{\AA}.
